### 로그인 (Admin 서비스에서 토큰 발급 — HR은 토큰 검증만 수행)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeEmail": "hrm@company.com",
  "password": "password123!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

###

### 평가 기간 생성 — 성공
POST http://localhost:8081/api/evaluation-periods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "algorithmVersionId": 1,
  "evalYear": 2026,
  "evalSequence": 1,
  "evalType": "QUALITATIVE",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31",
  "workerIds": [1, 2, 3]
}

###

### 평가 기간 생성 — 실패 (workerIds 누락, 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/evaluation-periods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "algorithmVersionId": 1,
  "evalYear": 2026,
  "evalSequence": 1,
  "evalType": "QUALITATIVE",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31",
  "workerIds": []
}

###

### 평가 기간 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/evaluation-periods/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "startDate": "2026-02-01",
  "endDate": "2026-04-30",
  "algorithmVersionId": 2
}

###

### 평가 기간 마감
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/evaluation-periods/1/close
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 평가 기간 확정
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/evaluation-periods/1/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
